videos.headline: Troy Williams fumbles on Utah's Opening Drive

videos.headline: Unretired RB scores TD in return to field
videos.description: Utah running back Joe Williams, who was retired at this point last week, bounces to the outside and runs in a 5-yard touchdown in the first quarter against Oregon State.

videos.headline: Williams fights to the corner to extend Utah's lead
